    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Park Brake Switch</title>
        <para>The Park Brake switch (see
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0404818">FIGURE 19</hotlnk>) is located on the dash. The ECU monitors the status of this
            switch. Whenever the switch is pushed in or pulled out the ECU responds by applying or releasing the parking
            brake. For complete system electrical diagrams, refer to the applicable ELECTRICAL CIRCUIT DIAGRAMS manual
            listed in ISIS. For information concerning troubleshooting the electrical circuits in the full power brakes
            system, refer to the applicable ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING guide listed in ISIS.
        </para>
